This is an adapter to Rainmeter. It ports Windows Rainmeter gadgets to
Linux Screenlets.


Implementation Details:

==== Skin Configs ====

  * BackgroundMode is ALWAYS considered to be 1, thus the following are
    NOT supported:
      
      Background, BackgroundMargins, SolidColor, SolidColor2, GradientAngle,
      BevelType
  
  * Update is SUPPORTED (Default to 1000, the same with Rainmeter)
  
  * DynamicWindowSize is ALWAYS ENABLED
  
  * DragMargins is NOT supported
  
  * KeepOnScreen is NOT supported
  
  * Author is IGNORED
  
  * AppVersion is IGNORED
  

